    <string name="onboarding_title_1">Privacy and Trust</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_1">SwiftSense is fully open-source. Your privacy is my priority, which is why the app never connects to the internet. All your data stays safely on your device.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_title_2">Advanced Tools</string>
    <string name="onboarding_desc_2">I\'ve gathered tools to optimize sensor rates and improve touch response in one place. Let\'s see what your hardware is truly capable of.</string>
